run(sql="
with cte as(
select dpYMD, pogId, guid from `last20Days(productView)` where pogId in ('621637793054','622702935255','624347216414','634304915124','636386805809','637813696220','647687860399','654264898661','658876063239')
order by pogId, dpYMD)
select distinct a.dpYMD, a.pogId, b.rawUrl from cte a left join `last20Days(sessionSummary)` b on a.guid=b.firstGuid where rawUrl is not null order by a.pogId, a.dpYMD
",1000)
